title: Turning data into actionable insights : A predictive Analytics with R
description:
We're happy to announce that our third meetup will take place this time at ENSIAS (The National School of Computer Science and Systems Analysis), Rabat.

Speakers:
- Sanae EL BERROUHI : https://www.linkedin.com/in/sanae-el-berrouhi-9026ab132/
- Adama Kalidou Diallo : https://www.linkedin.com/in/adama-kalidou-diallo/

#Time
- 9:30am arrival for a 10:00am start.

#What to bring
- The session will be hands on, so bring your own laptop with R and RStudio installed.

#Other
- Please confirm your attendance in meetup.com (places are limited).

The meetup will be in French.

For general discussions and to connect with other RLadies, join our Facebook group (https://www.facebook.com/groups/1517288175045425/).

We’re looking forward to meet you!

title: R from Scratch: Introduction and basics
description:
For those very new to R do not miss our second meetup where we will walk you through the basics of R and you will get some hands on experience with RStudio.

Everyone is welcome (beginner and advanced), No prior experience with programming is required.

• Proposed Schedule:

- 4pm - 4:30pm: Networking
- 4:30pm - 6:30pm: Workshop
- 6:30pm - 7pm: Closing and Networking

• What to bring
Please bring your laptop with R and RStudio installed.
Check out these 2 videos to see how to download and install (R and RStudio):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=riONFzJdXcs&list=PLqzoL9-eJTNBDdKgJgJzaQcY6OXmsXAHU
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cX532N_XLIs

• Important to know
Please arrive at 4:00 pm for a 4:30pm start.
